languages.text: "Что-нибудь ищете? Хотите купить, или, может, продать? Не стесняйтесь, спрашивайте — старая Ризза всякий народ знает. Мои ребятки вам все, что душе угодно, достанут!"

traits.locale_text: "Что-нибудь ищете? Хотите купить, или, может, продать? Не стесняйтесь, спрашивайте — старая Ризза всякий народ знает. Мои ребятки вам все, что душе угодно, достанут!"

languages.text: "Looking for something specific? You're buying, or maybe selling? Don't be shy, just ask — old Ryzza knows all kinds of folks. My boys will fetch you anything your heart desires!"

languages.text: “想找什么特别的东西吗？要买东西，还是要卖东西？别害羞，我就是随便问问。老莱萨认识各种各样的人，无论你想要什么东西，我的小伙子们都会帮你带来！”
languages.original_text: "Looking for something specific? You're buying, or maybe selling? Don't be shy, just ask — old Ryzza knows all kinds of folks. My boys will fetch you anything your heart desires!"

traits.locale_text: “想找什么特别的东西吗？要买东西，还是要卖东西？别害羞，我就是随便问问。老莱萨认识各种各样的人，无论你想要什么东西，我的小伙子们都会帮你带来！”

languages.text: «¿Busca algo concreto? ¿Comprar, o posiblemente vender? No sea tímido, pregunte. La vieja Ryzza conoce a gente de toda clase. ¡Mis muchachos pueden encontrar lo que su corazón ansía!».
languages.original_text: "Looking for something specific? You're buying, or maybe selling? Don't be shy, just ask — old Ryzza knows all kinds of folks. My boys will fetch you anything your heart desires!"

traits.locale_text: «¿Busca algo concreto? ¿Comprar, o posiblemente vender? No sea tímido, pregunte. La vieja Ryzza conoce a gente de toda clase. ¡Mis muchachos pueden encontrar lo que su corazón ansía!».

languages.text: 「何か特定のものをお探しかい？買うのも売るのも自由だ。遠慮しないで相談しな、このリザ様にかかればなんでも手に入るよ。何か欲しけりゃうちの部下に任せな！」
languages.original_text: "Looking for something specific? You're buying, or maybe selling? Don't be shy, just ask — old Ryzza knows all kinds of folks. My boys will fetch you anything your heart desires!"

languages.text: "Sucht Ihr was Bestimmtes? Wollt Ihr kaufen oder verkaufen? Seid nicht schüchtern, fragt einfach – die alte Ryzza kennt jede Menge Leute. Meine Jungs beschaffen Euch alles, was Euer Herz begehrt!"
languages.original_text: "Looking for something specific? You're buying, or maybe selling? Don't be shy, just ask — old Ryzza knows all kinds of folks. My boys will fetch you anything your heart desires!"

languages.text: « Vous cherchez quelque chose de précis ? Vous êtes là pour acheter, ou pour vendre ? Soyez pas timide, demandez... La vieille Ryzza connaît toutes sortes de gens. Mes gars peuvent vous dégotter tout ce dont vous rêvez ! »
languages.original_text: "Looking for something specific? You're buying, or maybe selling? Don't be shy, just ask — old Ryzza knows all kinds of folks. My boys will fetch you anything your heart desires!"

languages.text: "Var mı aradığın bir şey? Alıcı mısın yoksa satıcı mı? Hiç çekinme, aklında ne varsa söyle... Koca Ryzza'nın tanımadığı adam yoktur. Bizim oğlanlar her ne istersen bulur, getirir!"
